Class FragmentForecast.HandleWebCallListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.sdsmt.thompsonsamson.weatherapp.view.FragmentForecast.HandleWebCallListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IListeners
    Enclosing class:
    FragmentForecast

    public class FragmentForecast.HandleWebCallListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IListeners
    Handles calls back from the asynctasks. This will set the class members to the model objects _forecast and _forecastLocation. If an object was returned as null, we handle that as well by displaying some toast error. This implements the IListeners interface.
